### 1. ReactionButton Component (ReactionButton.jsx)

**Elements with CSS classes:**
- `.reaction-button-container` - wrapper div
- `.reaction-button` - main button
- `.reaction-button-emoji` - spans displaying the emoji
- `.reaction-count` - span showing count

**Event Handlers:**

| Handler | Trigger | Behavior |
|---------|---------|----------|
| `handleMouseEnter` | mouseenter | Sets 300ms timer to show picker |
| `handleMouseLeave` | mouseleave | Sets 150ms timer to hide picker |
| `handleTouchStart` | touchstart | Sets 500ms long-press timer to open picker (mobile) |
| `handleTouchEnd` | touchend | Clears long-press timer |
| `handleQuickClick` | onClick | Quick tap toggles reaction (removes if same, adds heart if none, or closes picker if open) |
| `handlePickerSelect` | (from ReactionPicker) | Called when user selects emoji from picker |

**Key Code Details:**
```javascript
const ReactionButton = ({ userReaction, reactionCount, onReact, disabled }) => {
    const [showPicker, setShowPicker] = useState(false);
    const hoverTimerRef = useRef(null);
    const leaveTimerRef = useRef(null);
    const longPressTimerRef = useRef(null);
    const longPressOpenedRef = useRef(false);

    const handleMouseEnter = useCallback(() => {
        // Clear leave timer if in progress
        if (leaveTimerRef.current) {
            clearTimeout(leaveTimerRef.current);
            leaveTimerRef.current = null;
        }
        // Set 300ms delay before showing picker
        hoverTimerRef.current = setTimeout(() => {
            setShowPicker(true);
        }, 300);
    }, []);

    const handleMouseLeave = useCallback(() => {
        if (hoverTimerRef.current) {
            clearTimeout(hoverTimerRef.current);
            hoverTimerRef.current = null;
        }
        // 150ms delay before hiding picker
        leaveTimerRef.current = setTimeout(() => {
            setShowPicker(false);
        }, 150);
    }, []);

    const handleTouchStart = useCallback(() => {
        // Long press: 500ms to show picker on mobile
        longPressTimerRef.current = setTimeout(() => {
            longPressOpenedRef.current = true;
            setShowPicker(true);
        }, 500);
    }, []);

    const handleTouchEnd = useCallback(() => {
        // Clear long press timer
        if (longPressTimerRef.current) {
            clearTimeout(longPressTimerRef.current);
            longPressTimerRef.current = null;
        }
    }, []);

    const handleQuickClick = useCallback((e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        if (disabled) return;

        // If picker was opened via long press, close it instead of reacting
        if (longPressOpenedRef.current) {
            longPressOpenedRef.current = false;
            return;
        }

        // If picker is open, just close it
        if (showPicker) {
            setShowPicker(false);
            return;
        }

        // Quick tap: toggle heart or remove current reaction
        if (userReaction) {
            onReact(userReaction); // toggle off
        } else {
            onReact('heart'); // default to heart
        }
    }, [userReaction, onReact, disabled, showPicker]);
```

**Cleanup:**
- useEffect runs on unmount to clear all pending timers

